---
title: Sweet Chili and Sesame Turkey with Garlic Rice and Bok Choy
description: We’ve fired up this sizzling stir-fry with sweet chili and sesame turkey.  Garlicky rice and bok choy round out this weeknight winner!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/sweet-chili-and-sesame-turkey-adb741f1.jpg
